snippet.title: Anime Zodiac Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: Hello! There are twelve of us, we are all sweet girls, and we are waiting to meet you! Each of us has his own character and unique appearance (except for the twins (they are the same)). All the girls are waiting for the opportunity to tell about themselves in Anime Zodiac. And what is your zodiac sign?
